## Can also do logistic regression



::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code}
tbl_uvregression(
  nlsy, 
  y = glasses,
  include = c(sex_cat, race_eth_cat,
              eyesight_cat, glasses, age_bir),
  method = glm,
  method.args = list(family = binomial()),
  exponentiate = TRUE)
```

